OL,6,FA father accused of murdering his five-
OL,7,Fweek-old baby son in has been found
OL,8,Fguilty.
OL,10,FThe baby's mother was cleared of
OL,11,Fmurder but found guilty of causing or
OL,12,Fallowing her son's death.
OL,14,FThe jury was told how was found
OL,15,Flifeless in his crib at home in
OL,16,FBeaumont Leys on the morning of 21
OL,17,FOctober in 2017, having sustained
OL,18,Ffractures to his skull, collar bone,
OL,19,Fboth arms and the joints of all his
OL,20,Flimbs.
