OL,6,FHe was taken by ambulance to where he
OL,7,Fdied later that day, despite the
OL,8,Fefforts of medics.
OL,10,FMichael Davis, 29, was found guilty of
OL,11,Fmurder and two counts of causing
OL,12,Fgrievous bodily harm and was remanded
OL,13,Fin custody facing a mandatory life
OL,14,Fsentence.
