OL,6,FJurors cleared Ollie's mother,
OL,7,FKayleigh Driver, 31, of murder and
OL,8,Fcausing grievous bodily harm with
OL,9,Fintent, but found her guilty of
OL,10,Fcharges of causing or allowing the
OL,11,Fdeath of a child and causing or
OL,12,Fallowing serious physical injury.
OL,14,FTrial judge Mr Justice Cotter renewed
OL,15,FDriver's conditional bail following
OL,16,Fthe verdicts and ordered that she
OL,17,Fshould be sentenced alongside Davis on
OL,18,FApril 10.
