OL,6,FAdjourning the case, Mr Justice Cotter
OL,7,Ftold Davis: "The position is that, by
OL,8,Fvirtue of the verdicts of this jury,
OL,9,Fthere is only one sentence which I can
OL,10,Fpass, which is a life sentence.
OL,12,F"However the minimum term you will
OL,13,Fserve remains to be determined."
OL,15,FThe judge then told Driver: "You have
OL,16,Fbeen convicted of serious offences.
OL,17,FThere will inevitably be a custodial
OL,18,Fsentence, the length of which I will
OL,19,Fdetermine on April 10."
