OL,6,FAfter thanking the jury for its
OL,7,Fservice during the "difficult and
OL,8,Fdemanding" case, the judge excused the
OL,9,Fpanel from undertaking jury service
OL,10,Ffor the next 20 years.
OL,12,FPolice say there were no obvious signs
OL,13,Fof injury or any illness that could
OL,14,Faccount for Ollie's death, but a few
OL,15,Fdays later, following medical
OL,16,Finvestigation, the true extent of the
OL,17,Fbaby's injuries was uncovered.
