OL,6,FOpening the Crown's case in January,
OL,7,Fprosecutor Jonas Hankin KC told
OL,8,Fjurors: "The case concerns the death
OL,9,Fof five-week-old Ollie Davis on the
OL,10,Fmorning of the October 21, 2017.
OL,12,F"He was found lifeless in his crib in
OL,13,Fthe bedroom that he shared with his
OL,14,Fparents at Upper Temple Walk here in
OL,15,FLeicester.
