OL,6,FSpeaking in a police interview in
OL,7,F2017, Michael Davis said his son
OL,8,F"seemed and looked fine" and he
OL,9,F"wasn't sure" how he had obtained the
OL,10,Finjuries.
OL,12,F"I'm quite shocked by them to be
OL,13,Fhonest", he added.
OL,15,FAlongside the examination of his
OL,16,Finjuries by a number of medical
OL,17,Fspecialists, Leicestershire Police
OL,18,Fcontinued to interview Driver and
OL,19,FDavis, as well as their family members
OL,20,Fand health care professionals.
