OL,6,FThe pair both continued to deny any
OL,7,Fknowledge of what had happened to
OL,8,Ftheir son.
OL,10,FIn October 2021, after four years of
OL,11,Fgathering evidence, Davis and Driver
OL,12,Fwere charged in connection with
OL,13,FOllie's death and causing other
OL,14,Finjuries.
OL,16,FDI Mark Parish of said: "Today's
OL,17,Fverdicts are the culmination of more
OL,18,Fthan six years of police investigation
OL,19,Fand detailed medical examination by
OL,20,Fspecialists.
