OL,7,Fthe investigation and prosecution team
OL,8,Fhas been in vital in achieving today's
OL,9,Fresult. We never lost sight in how
OL,10,Fimportant it was to get justice for
OL,11,FOllie."
OL,13,FDC Batstone added: "Davis and Driver
OL,14,Fhave evaded justice since 2017 but
OL,15,Fwill now be facing a lengthy sentence
OL,16,Ffor their actions. Ollie was a
OL,17,Fdefenceless newborn baby who was
OL,18,Fabused and ultimately killed by
OL,19,Fsomeone who should have protected and
OL,20,Fcared for him the most.
